query:
-- Primeiro, vamos ver quais ambientes da vistoria 1 não têm inspection_items
SELECT 
  e.id as environment_id,
  e.name as environment_name,
  ii.id as inspection_item_id
FROM environments e
LEFT JOIN inspection_items ii ON (e.id = ii.environment_id AND ii.inspection_id = 1)
WHERE e.project_id = 1
ORDER BY e.name;
